Appendices

Appendix A ‚Äì Environment Variables

Variable	Purpose

NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTRACT_ADDRESS	Deployed WhisperLedger contract address.
ARBITRUM_RPC_URL	WebSocket RPC endpoint for Chronicler.
DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN	Bot auth token (secret).
HALL_OF_WEAVERS_CHANNEL_ID	Discord channel for solve announcements.

Appendix B ‚Äì Riddle Creation Framework

1. Concept Seed ‚Üí physical phenomenon / abstract metaphor.


2. Constraint Layer ‚Üí syllabic rhythm, internal rhyme, misdirection.


3. Signal Words ‚Üí 2‚Äì3 subtle hints; avoid overfitting to brute-force keyword guesses.


4. Ambiguity Check ‚Üí ensure only one clean plausible answer.


5. Blind Review ‚Üí test with 3 external readers (time-to-first-answer metric).


6. Catalog Tagging ‚Üí theme, tier, expected solve time, fallback hint.



Appendix C ‚Äì Tokenomics Considerations (To Finalize Post-Audit)

Allocation	%	Notes

Genesis Liquidity	X%	Seeded & locked ‚â• 12m.
Treasury	X%	Governance‚Äëcontrolled (development, audits).
Verse Emissions	X%	Capped; schedule of decreasing rewards per season.
Community Incentives	X%	Art collabs, lore NFTs, hackathons.
Team / Advisors	X%	Linear vesting (e.g., 24m, 6m cliff).

Appendix D ‚Äì Governance Evolution Path

1. Council Multi-Sig (Phase 1‚Äì2) ‚Äì Operational safety only.


2. Snapshot Signalling (Phase 3) ‚Äì Off-chain proposals; multi-sig executes.


3. Delegated Voting (Phase 4) ‚Äì Introduce lightweight Governor contract for treasury + verse parameters (reward caps).


4. Modular Verse Registry (Phase 5) ‚Äì DAO parameterizes verse cadence, difficulty weight multipliers.



Appendix E ‚Äì Visual & Brand Motifs

Element	Direction

Primary Glyph	M√∂bius strip + subtle ear / spiral echo.
Palette	Obsidian (#0D0D12), Whisper Violet (#7E4DDA), Ember Accent (#FFB347), Soft Gray (#8A8FA3).
Typography	Serif (display) + geometric mono (code / verse).
Motion	Slow rotational parallax; emphasize quiet resonance.
Sound Design	Soft triad chimes (C‚ÄìE‚ÄìG) modulated by verse ‚Äòresonance‚Äô.


