2	Outer ring + soft glow (#6DBF89 30%)	Elevated grace
3	Dual ring (#6DBF89 + #FFB347)	Creation tier
4	Pulsing halo (slow 6s)	High stewardship
5	Animated gradient halo + subtle glyph ‚ú∂	Rare anchor

