9.1 loomctl CLI Stub (TypeScript)

Purpose: Execute YAML checklists (Part VIII), capture operator inputs, persist signed run logs, and emit optional attestations.

a. Directory Structure

loomctl/
‚îú‚îÄ package.json
‚îú‚îÄ tsconfig.json
‚îú‚îÄ src/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ index.ts            # entrypoint (bin)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ commands/
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ run.ts          # run checklist
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ list.ts         # list checklists
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ attest.ts       # emit EAS attestation for completed run
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ core/
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ loader.ts       # YAML load & schema validate
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ executor.ts     # interactive runner
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ signer.ts       # local private key / keystore integration
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ log.ts          # structured JSONL writer
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ hash.ts         # content hashing (keccak256)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ types.ts
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ config.ts
‚îî‚îÄ checklists/ (mounted or provided path)

b. package.json (excerpt)

{
"name": "@whisperledger/loomctl",
"version": "0.1.0",
"type": "module",
"bin": { "loomctl": "dist/index.js" },
"scripts": { "build": "tsc -p .", "dev": "ts-node src/index.ts" },
